  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Urdu words 'Lafz' and 'Alfaaz'?",
  "response": "In Urdu, the word **'Lafz'** (\u0644\u0641\u0638) means \"word.\" It refers to a single unit of language that conveys meaning. \n\nThe term **'Alfaaz'** (\u0627\u0644\u0641\u0627\u0638) is the plural form of 'Lafz' and means \"words\" or \"expressions.\" It is often used to refer to multiple words or to discuss language and vocabulary in a broader context.\n\nBoth terms are commonly used in literature, poetry, and everyday conversation in Urdu.",
